Package com.hds.aw.auto.reportingApi.sdk.interfaces.audit

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AccountActivityReport
    Reports all account activity of the audited user(s).
    AuditReport  
    FileModificationsMadeByUsersReport
    Reports file and folder modifications performed by a user, including modifications performed by a user on files and folders owned by other users.
    FileReadsMadeByUsersReport
    Reports all files and folders accessed by a user, including reads made by a user on files owned by other users.
    LinkActivityReport
    Reports all link activity of the audited user(s).
    LinkReadsMadeByUsersReport
    Reports all files and folders on which the user performed an authenticated read through a link.
    LinkReadsOnFilesOwnedByUsersReport
    Reports each time a file or folder that the user(s) owned was accessed through a link.
    LinkReadsOnSpecificFileReport
    Reports all link reads to the specified path of the audited user(s), including link reads made by other users if the file or folder resides in a shared or Team Folder.
    ModificationsOnFilesOwnedByUsersReport
    Reports all modifications performed on files and folders owned by a user.
    ModificationsOnSpecificFileReport
    Reports all modifications to the specified path of the user(s), including modifications made by other users if the file or folder resides in a shared or Team folder.
    ReadsOnFilesOwnedByUsersReport
    Reports each time a file or folder that the user owned was accessed, including reads by other users of shared files and folders that are owned by the audited user(s).
    ReadsOnSpecificFileReport
    Reports all reads to the specified path of the audited user(s), including reads made by other users if the file or folder resides in a shared or Team folder.
    ShareActivityReport
    Reports all share activity of a specified user.
